      <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 16px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">What is concepts.?</h3>
        <p>concepts. is a microlearning app that delivers powerful mental models in just 2 minutes a day. Each concept includes a clear explanation, a counterintuitive insight, and actionable steps you can apply today.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">How does the subscription work?</h3>
        <p>Start with a free 3-day trial. After that, it's just $0.99/week. You can cancel anytime through your device's subscription settings. All subscriptions are managed through Apple App Store or Google Play Store.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">How do I manage my subscription?</h3>
        <p><strong>On iOS:</strong> Go to Settings > [Your Name] > Subscriptions, then select concepts. to manage or cancel.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 8px;"><strong>On Android:</strong> Open Google Play Store > Menu > Subscriptions, then select concepts. to manage or cancel.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">How do I restore my purchases?</h3>
        <p>Open the app and go to Settings. Tap "Restore Purchases" to restore your subscription on a new device or after reinstalling the app.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">How many concepts can I generate per day?</h3>
        <p>Free users can generate up to 3 concepts per day. This limit resets daily based on your timezone. Pro subscribers have unlimited access to all concepts in the feed.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">Can I use concepts. offline?</h3>
        <p>Yes! Once you've viewed a concept, it's saved locally and you can read it offline. However, generating new concepts requires an internet connection.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">How do I delete my account?</h3>
        <p>Go to Settings in the app and tap "Delete Account". This will permanently delete your account and all associated data. This action cannot be undone.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">I'm having trouble signing in with Apple</h3>
        <p>Make sure you're using the same Apple ID that you used to sign up. If you're still having issues, try signing out of your Apple ID on your device and signing back in, then try again in the app.</p>
      </div>
